@bendem Does docker have a syntax for tag ? We might need a new syntax for `tag` so that buildah can pre-hand know if this is a tag,  see https://github.com/containers/buildah/pull/4149

Maybe new syntax could be 
`buildah build -t test myrepo.git#*<some-tag>`

@containers/buildah-maintainers WDYT
